Class AbstractEventDistributor<T extends HasMetadata>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microbean.kubernetes.controller.AbstractEventDistributor<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Consumer<EventQueue<T>>

    public abstract class AbstractEventDistributor<T extends HasMetadata>
extends Object
implements Consumer<EventQueue<T>>
    An abstract Consumer of EventQueues, particularly suitable for supplying to the EventQueueCollection.start(Consumer) method, whose implementations can distribute Events in some fashion.
    Author:
    Laird Nelson
    See Also:
    EventQueue, EventQueueCollection.start(Consumer)
